    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2008-06-10</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2008-07-22T18:14:53Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Working Families Gas Tax Credit Act of 2008 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a tax credit for up to $500 ($1,000 in the case of a joint return) of the cost of gasoline and diesel used in highway vehicles for a nonbusiness purpose when the increase in the price of a gallon of gasoline exceeds the annual inflation rate by not less than 300%. Phases out the amount of such credit for taxpayers with adjusted gross incomes exceeding $75,000 ($150,000 in the case of a joint return). </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
